<h2>Ordering From Amazon?</h2><p>Ensure you get a VAT Receipt, it means we can claim back the VAT which will save your sport / society / event money.</p><p>To Do So:</p><ol><li>Go to your&nbsp;<a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/css/history/orders/view.html" target="_blank">Order History</a>.</li><li>Find your order.</li><li>Click "Invoice" on the right hand side next to that order.</li><li>You may have the option "Print Invoice", click this. It may say&nbsp;"Invoice not available" in which case we are unable to claim back the VAT.</li><li>On the new page save the pdf file &#40;Ctrl + S&#41; then upload it on this page.</li></ol>